summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 2069, for the improvement of the alley between blocks 3 and 4, Crown Addition to the City of Seattle; by grading the same and providing for the necessary surface drainage, under Ordinance No. 20820 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against each parcel of land and part thereof shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof.
